      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "For sale is an enthusiast-maintained E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. This specimen has received critical preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to address known chassis fatigue. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission operates with precision, paired with a variable M-differential lock for superior power delivery. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and upgraded bushings, maintaining factory geometry while sharpening turn-in response. Though it exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-driven machine, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain harmonics are exceptional.",
