    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that perfectly balances luxury and performance. The exterior is finished in a deep Midnight Blue Metallic that shines beautifully in the sun, though I want to be transparent about a few minor rock chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with premium tan leather upholstery. The seats are in great shape, with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it has received synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the brake pads and rotors were recently replaced. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and quiet ride for the next owner. It shifts flawlessly and handles with precision. This is a reliable, attractive vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
