      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a brand new home! This car has been so good to me\u2014it's super reliable, drives smoothly, and is in really solid shape. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics. Come tuck it into your driveway and take it for a spin! \u2728",
