    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an E46 M3 equipped with the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system recently serviced for optimal cam timing. This chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement to ensure torsional rigidity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides precise engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior power delivery out of corners. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering feel this platform is known for. While the aesthetic shows honest patina from spirited use, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain harmonics are excellent, making this a superb driver-spec example for the serious enthusiast.",
